cs.SE, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.PL. 

The paper deals with automated correction of syntax errors in programming assignments using Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SE (Software Engineering), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper uses language models to learn valid token sequences. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with programming assignments, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages).
